snippet.title: Best VGM 1466 - Shin Megami Tensei IV - Ikebukuro Underground District
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1679 - http://youtu.be/a_qDMzn6BOA
Best VGM 1854 - https://youtu.be/LcFX7lFjfqA

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

3DS
Shin Megami Tensei IV (2013)
Ikebukuro Underground District
Ryota Koduka
